Author: ImDemandingARefund
Text: Not POAO related but I think I kinda feel this way I don’t eat anything that comes from a box, bag, or similar. I’m aware it’s psychological.

Author: Tiny_Buttercups98
Text: I feel this when I'm fasting or high restricting I wont say by how much just in case, but yeah my friend. I get it. As weird as it sounds after a few days it feels like I've just gotten out of a hot shower after being unclean for a long time if that makes sense.  Like I get more into my baths, I keep up with my skincare routine, i drink a crazy amount of water and keep my room super clean.  I dont know why though, it's a weird one
